title: Need Help Finding a Rental in Round Rock?
posting_body: ["Hi my name is Travis and I'm am a Realtor here in Austin.", 'I have 29 years experience in this city as I was born and raised here.', 'This would make me an excellent choice to help you and your family find a rental in Austin or surrounding areas.', "Even making things easier by setting you up on automated emails from my MLS portal to find exactly what you're looking for.", '- Reach out to me and provide me your move in timeframe, budget, and any other special requirements.', '- We can set up a day to go tour the properties.', 'If your not here locally, not problem!', 'We can schedule a FaceTime tour.', "**Please don't hesitate to reach out!", 'My services come at no cost to you**', 'You can reach out to me through a call or text at ( 51 2) 68', '9- 791 8', 'Travis Lee']
